      "content": "Encharge is a behavior-based marketing automation platform built for SaaS companies. The REST API exposes the core resources used by integrations: people, fields, segments, tags, event subscriptions (webhooks), and account information. Authentication uses the X-Encharge-Token header. Also documented here: the Ingest API for backend event submission and the Transactional Email API for templated and custom HTML/text email.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Encharge Developer Documentation",
